，自由對佢地都係啲可有可無嘅嘢。有果時，took it for granted；冇果時，都係唔會挺起腰骨fight for it"},{"pid":"77518aada48dc9ba87f29673613e6ed3b35840f7","tid":2410904,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0d38d383d615b41f1c5b5f135e162a1ea2e1ff4","tid":2410904,"uid":59030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"點解釋北角book到三月都無期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"藍屍：飢餓行銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4772e09f7d50a40f43c89c5a45a9775b05b264","tid":2410904,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"想當年信咗你唔買樓走去買匯豐嗰個<br />\n唔知今次會唔會再信你呢"},{"pid":"98806b55deac6803220e61a30d376a273af001b5","tid":2410904,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:23:43.000Z","msg":"下年疫情受控先見真章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834b686a328835030befd8776d76e3deef7732e4","tid":2410904,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"個app都未開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a712b220eed5a6f39aede1d2f20ae330a10e07","tid":2410904,"uid":37874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b26cf1f685cf96f5619202ded8d431d18133caf","tid":2410904,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7335199d8dee9f430cd6b00d4373aa23e84a435","tid":2410904,"uid":18477,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200808/share_2020080818493163239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200808%2Fshare_2020080818493163239.jpg&h=a3c6098d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2KJS8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail